node.text:
First time doing legends hair and it’s safe to say the @curls poppin pineapple collection did the job. Queen has been using @curls and hyping it for awhile so I had to try for myself. I love the way it makes our hair look and smell
•
Waves on swim ✅
Curls on pop ✅
Smell on 10 ✅
•
Definitely recommend to all of my curly and textured hair followers. You won’t be disappointed
•
where to buy: @walmart and online at curls.biz. 

Use code “curlslovesyou20” for 20% off your order 🍍

#curlspartner #poppinpineapple #ultimatestylingcollection #naturalcurls #washandgo #washandgotutorial #curlyhairtutorial #curlyhairstyle #naturalhairtutorial #blueberrybliss #ultimatestylingchallenge

node.text:
First time doing legends hair and it’s safe to say the @curls poppin pineapple collection did the job. Queen has been using @curls and hyping it for awhile so I had to try for myself. I love the way it makes our hair look and smell
•
Waves on swim ✅
Curls on pop ✅
Smell on 10 ✅
•
Definitely recommend to all of my curly and textured hair followers. You won’t be disappointed
•
where to buy: @walmart and online at curls.biz. 

Use code “curlslovesyou20” for 20% off your order 🍍
